# Prompt Used to Generate the Investment Memo

This prompt was used with Claude to generate the final Word document 
(`NSCLC_Investment_Memo.docx`) from my SQL, Excel, and Power BI outputs. 
It's structured to keep the AI grounded in my actual data rather than 
letting it invent figures — every number is sourced from attached files, 
